title: Amazing Dr. Clitterhouse (1938) Edward G. Robinson Humphrey Boga
description:
Odd mixture of screwball comedy and film noir; you get to see Bogart and Robinson. Edward G. Robinson really impressed me in The Sea Wolf, how this diminutive actor managed to portray the giant Wolf Larsen through sheer acting ability. It's worth checking out anything he's in, and he certainly does a nice job here.

"a fascinating film in many ways" - Aw-komon, IMDb.
